snippet.title: OVRLRD Trailer #2 | June 2024
snippet.description:
OVRLRD is the definitive VR mech simulator, coming to PCVR and Quest this year. Free demo available on Steam right now!

https://steampowered.com/app/2163160/

Music is 'Ground Assault' from the OVRLRD OST, composed by Samuel Lilly:
https://soundcloud.com/samthefearful/ovrlrd-ost-ground-assault

Join the official OVRLRD discord:
https://discord.gg/geTFDs4wYD
